

$Frm->uhdr("ORAC_OBSERVATION_MODE" => "ifu");


# Podule
# ======

=head1 Name

_SPECTROSCOPY_MODE_ -- switches observation mode to ifu 

=head1 Description

Switches observation mode to ifu, used after switching it to spectroscopy
to allow IFU recipes to use conventional spectroscopy primitives.

=head1 Authors

Stephen P. Todd (Edinburgh University/UKATC)

